      "text": "お仕事楽しかった～～！\nあ、そうだ！　この辺にドーナツ屋さんがあるんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Work was fun~~!\nOh‚ right! There's a donut shop around here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
