      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9207256634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、一緒に食べに行こ！\nドーナツドーナツ！　ドードードーナツ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ let's go eat together!\nDonut donut! Do-do-donut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9207256634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.4646936416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、私もちょうど、甘いものが食べたい気分だし\n付き合おうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I feel like eating something sweet‚ too\nShall we go together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4646936416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6970972378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "やった～！　じゃあ早速しゅっぱーつ！\nれっつ、ごーなっつ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Then‚ let's go right nowー!\nLet's go-nut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6970972378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.577049605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
