      "text": "そんなにドーナツが食べたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wanted to eat donuts so much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.577049605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1253488381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "どれから食べようかな～！　やっぱり新発売の\n米粉を使った、コメッコ・リングかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I eat first~! As I expected‚ it's the newly released\nKomekko Rings made with rice flour",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1753488381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.7498836994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "って、あれ？　琴乃ちゃん、二個しか食べないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ wait? Kotono-chan‚ you only ate two?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7498836994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.3407678922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "もっと食べたいけど、カロリーが気になっちゃって\n二個でも多いとは思うんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to eat more‚ but I'm concerned about calories\nI think two is too many…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3407678922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.3055977822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、芽衣とゲームしようよ！\nじゃんけんで勝った方が、ドーナツを一個食べれるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let's play a game with Mei!\nWhoever wins rock-paper-scissors gets to eat a donut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3055977822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9146909397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら沢山食べちゃっても、罪悪感ないんじゃない？\n運が良かったんだ～って思えるし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ you won't feel guilty even if you eat a lot?\nJust think~ I was lucky!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9146909397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2682053566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうものかな……？　でも、面白そう\n芽衣のが四個で、私のが二個だから、六回勝負ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…? Still‚ it looks fun\nMei has four and I have two‚ so it's a six-round match",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2682053566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.4533976872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふー、果たして何個食べられるかな～？\nじゃあいくよー！　じゃん、けん、ぽん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heheheー‚ how many can I eat~?\nHere we goー! Rock‚ paper‚ scissors!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4533976872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.5999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4576039949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ん～、おいひい……三個目はちょっと罪悪感があるけど\n運が良かったから、仕方ないわよね。うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ it's good… I feel a little guilty about third one though\nI was lucky‚ so it is what it is. Yeah",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4762059846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3305595714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅー、芽衣も食べたいよー\nなんで一回も勝てないんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oohー‚ Mei want to eat‚ tooー\nWhy can't I win even once…",
