      "text": "そう言って琴乃ちゃん、さっきチョキ出したよね……\n「じゃんけんは心理戦だから」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying that‚ Kotono-chan‚ you took out scissors just now…\n'Rock-paper-scissors is a psychological game'‚ you said…",
        "id": ""
