      "text": "じゃんけんぽん……あ……私の勝ち……？\n何個目だっけ、これ……もう、限界なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rock-paper-scissors… ah… my victory…?\nHow many of these have I got‚ I can't… stand‚ anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
