      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ！　琴乃ちゃん、もう一回やろ！\n芽衣、追加のドーナツ買ってくるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! Kotono-chan‚ one more time!\nMei‚ will buy some more donuts!",
